{
  "texts": [
    "To test this, we use patients from the test set in the gold-standard dataset.",
    "Recall that in our context processing step in Section Note enrichment, we remove notes that do not contain any IDU keywords.",
    "For this analysis, we incorporate 443 notes from 226 patients with no mentions of IDU keywords.",
    "We ensure that the notes only belong to the patients in the test set.",
    "To annotate these notes, we use the query group-existence of IDUas questions and empty strings as answers."
  ]
}